data.title: Pilar Wayne
data.meta_description: Pilar Wayne. Actress: Sabotear en la selva. Pilar Wayne was born on 3 September 1928 in Peru. She is an actress, known for Sabotear en la selva (1953), The Hollywood Greats (1977) and Live! On City Line (1987). She was previously married to Jesse L. Upchurch, Stephan Steward, John Wayne and Richard Weldy.
